source.sqlReaderQuery:
SELECT 
hd.[SalesOrderID],
hd.[OrderDate],
hd.[CustomerID],
hd.[SubTotal],
hd.[TaxAmt],
hd.[Freight],
hd.[TotalDue],
dt.[OrderQty],
dt.[ProductID],
dt.[UnitPrice],
dt.[UnitPriceDiscount],
dt.[LineTotal]
FROM [SalesLT].[SalesOrderHeader] AS hd 
INNER JOIN [SalesLT].[SalesOrderDetail] AS dt
ON hd.[SalesOrderID] = dt.[SalesOrderID]

scriptLines: SelectColumns derive(TotalDue = add(Freight, add(SubTotal, TaxAmt))) ~> DerivedTotalDue
details as (mobile as string, city as string)
